/a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/WindSekirun/SectionCalendarView?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=6807\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/WindSekirun/SectionCalendarView</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/Team-Blox/TreeView?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=6779\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Team-Blox/TreeView</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/Angads25/android-toggle?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=6778\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Angads25/android-toggle</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/florent37/ShapeOfView?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=6782\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/florent37/ShapeOfView</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"http://github.com/mreram/TicketView?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=6799\" target=\"_blank\">http://github.com/mreram/TicketView</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/kevalpatel2106/android-hidden-camera\">https://github.com/kevalpatel2106/android-hidden-camera</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/levitnudi/LegacyTableView?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=6819\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/levitnudi/LegacyTableView</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/jkennethcarino/RTextEditorView?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=6207\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/jkennethcarino/RTextEditorView</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/m7mdra/HtmlRecycler?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7092\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/m7mdra/HtmlRecycler</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/airbnb/lottie-android\">https://github.com/airbnb/lottie-android</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/Blankj/AndroidUtilCode\">https://github.com/Blankj/AndroidUtilCode</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/orhanobut/logger\">https://github.com/orhanobut/logger</a></li><li> <a href=\"https://github.com/iamporus/TypedTextView\">https://github.com/iamporus/TypedTextView</a> </li><li> <a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7687\">https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7687</a> </li><li> <a href=\"https://github.com/bkhezry/weather\">https://github.com/bkhezry/weather</a> </li><li></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Refrence: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://android-arsenal.com/</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/?page=21&amp;sort=created\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://android-arsenal.com/?page=21&amp;sort=created</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Libs And Tools','','publish','open','open','','libs-and-tools','','','2019-06-21 13:47:51','2019-06-21 12:47:51','',0,'http://blogs.appsfeature.com/?p=201',0,'post','',0),(202,1,'2019-01-05 09:41:13','2019-01-05 09:41:13','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7357\">EasyFlipViewPager</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/book_flip_demo.gif?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7357\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/poker_demo.gif?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7357\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/gallery_demo.gif?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7357\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><h2></h2><br><img width=\"280px\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/gallery_demo.gif\"></a><img width=\"280px\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/poker_demo.gif\"><img width=\"280px\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/book_flip_demo.gif\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7359\">Hauler</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Hauler is a library containing custom layout which enables to easily create swipe to dismiss <code>Activity</code>. Implementation is based on code from project <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/nickbutcher/plaid?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7359\" target=\"_blank\">Plaid</a>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/thefuntasty/hauler\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/thefuntasty/hauler</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thefuntasty/hauler/master/images/example.gif\">\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7362\">Easy CSV</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Creates csv file for android </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/hsmnzaydn/easy-csv\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/hsmnzaydn/easy-csv</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7364\">Text Scanner from image</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> This library extend <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://developers.google.com/vision/?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7364\" target=\"_blank\">google vision</a> . And initilay it read text from image. for reading text from image you have to give image <strong>Uri</strong> or <strong>Bitmap</strong>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/mahimrocky/TextRecognizer\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/mahimrocky/TextRecognizer</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mahimrocky/TextRecognizer/master/screenshot.png\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7366\">Choreographer</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Animate views easily by chaining animations, run them serially or in parallel. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/ZachBublil/Choreographer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/ZachBublil/Choreographer</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ZachBublil/Choreographer/master/demoGif.gif\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7367\">BottomSheetTimeRangePicker</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>BottomSheetPickers is a tiny Android library for adding Date and Time Pickers as Modal BottomSheetDialogs with From and To ranges.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The library is inspired by Titto Jose\'s <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/tittojose/TimeRangePicker?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7367\" target=\"_blank\">TimeRangePicker</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/adawoud/BottomSheetTimeRangePicker\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/adawoud/BottomSheetTimeRangePicker</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adawoud/BottomSheetTimeRangePicker/master/art/bottomsheetpicker.png\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7376\">android-imagecropview</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> A