opener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/book_flip_demo.gif?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7357\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/poker_demo.gif?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7357\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/gallery_demo.gif?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7357\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><h2></h2><br><img width=\"280px\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/gallery_demo.gif\"></a><img width=\"280px\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/poker_demo.gif\"><img width=\"280px\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/book_flip_demo.gif\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7359\">Hauler</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Hauler is a library containing custom layout which enables to easily create swipe to dismiss&nbsp;<code>Activity</code>. Implementation is based on code from project&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/nickbutcher/plaid?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7359\" target=\"_blank\">Plaid</a>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/thefuntasty/hauler\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/thefuntasty/hauler</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n \n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thefuntasty/hauler/master/images/example.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:300px;\"></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7362\">Easy CSV</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Creates csv file for android </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/hsmnzaydn/easy-csv\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/hsmnzaydn/easy-csv</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7364\">Text Scanner from image</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> This library extend&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://developers.google.com/vision/?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7364\" target=\"_blank\">google vision</a>&nbsp;. And initilay it read text from image. for reading text from image you have to give image&nbsp;<strong>Uri</strong>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<strong>Bitmap</strong>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/mahimrocky/TextRecognizer\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/mahimrocky/TextRecognizer</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mahimrocky/TextRecognizer/master/screenshot.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:300px;\"></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7366\">Choreographer</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Animate views easily by chaining animations, run them serially or in parallel. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/ZachBublil/Choreographer\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/ZachBublil/Choreographer</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ZachBublil/Choreographer/master/demoGif.gif\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7367\">BottomSheetTimeRangePicker</a></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>BottomSheetPickers is a tiny Android library for adding Date and Time Pickers as Modal BottomSheetDialogs with From and To ranges.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The library is inspired by Titto Jose\'s&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/tittojose/TimeRangePicker?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7367\" target=\"_blank\">TimeRangePicker</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/adawoud/BottomSheetTimeRangePicker\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/adawoud/BottomSheetTimeRangePicker</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adawoud/BottomSheetTimeRangePicker/master/art/bottomsheetpicker.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:300px;\"></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7376\">android-imagecropview</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> An Android library that lets you implement image crop. ImageCropView crops image by moving image under fixed crop area like instagram and iOS. Image zoom in/out is base on&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/sephiroth74/ImageViewZoom?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7376\" target=\"_blank\">sephiroth74\'s imageViewZoom. Sample app is base on&nbsp;</a><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://developers.aviary.com/?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7376\" target=\"_blank\">aviary SDK sample.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/naver/android-imagecropview\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/naver/android-imagecropview</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/naver/android-imagecropview/master/doc/img/pholar.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:300px;\"></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7417\">Payment Card View</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/manojbhadane/PaymentCardView\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/manojbhadane/PaymentCardView</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/manojbhadane/PaymentCardView/master/PaymentCardView.png\" alt=\"\"/><figcaption><br></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7407\">Dynamic Toasts</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/hotstu/ZebraTextView\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/hotstu/ZebraTextView</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> A simple library to display themed toasts with icon and text on Android 9+ (Gingerbread or above) devices. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/pranavpandey/dynamic-toasts/master/graphics/dynamic-toasts-preview.png\" alt=\"\"/><figcaption><br></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7401\">Material Toast</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/marcoscgdev/MaterialToast\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/marcoscgdev/MaterialToast</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nA fully and highly customizable material designed Toast for Android.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/marcoscgdev/MaterialToast/master/device-2018-12-22-164932.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:300px;\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1> <a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7351\">StateViews</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/kobeumut/StateViews\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/kobeumut/StateViews</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Create &amp; Show progress, data or error views, the easy way! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kobeumut/StateViews/master/art/StatusPage.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7334\">Country code dialog picker</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/BartNijland91/android-countrycodepickerdialog\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/BartNijland91/android-countrycodepickerdialog</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BartNijland91/android-countrycodepickerdialog/master/screenshot.png\" alt=\"\"style=\"width:300px;\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7340\">Cyanea</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/jaredrummler/Cyanea\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/jaredrummler/Cyanea</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nA powerful, dynamic, and fun theme engine. Named after Octopus Cyanea which is adept at camouflage and not only can change color frequently, but also can change the patterns on and texture of its skin.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\">\n<a>\n<img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/7f7f7520d61f2f704ff12d6d31b7cafe601263e4/68747470733a2f2f692e696d6775722e636f6d2f6543366435574f2e676966\" alt=\"\"/>\n</a>\n<a>\n<img align=\"left\" hspace=\"10\" src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/b0cdc1242d8170b8184ef2a92d8afd5af4152563/68747470733a2f2f692e696d6775722e636f6d2f706a44456a576c2e676966\">\n</a>\n</figure> \n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/3/7342\">CurvedBottomNavigationView</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/androidtutorialonline/CurvedBottomNavigationView\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/androidtutorialonline/CurvedBottomNavigationView</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nwe will learn How to draw custom shapes in Curved Bottom Navigation View\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/7cf1dee61362f29a0abd06248d8b439a5323130f/68747470733a2f2f7777772e616e64726f69647475746f7269616c6f6e6c696e652e636f6d2f77702d636f6e74656e742f75706c6f6164732f323031382f31312f426f74746f6d4e617669676174696f6e566965772e676966\" alt=\"enter image description here\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7350\">FloatingToast</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/hariprasanths/FloatingToast\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/hariprasanths/FloatingToast</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nAn android library to make customisable floating animated toasts\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/b469bd7e9f684420b89eab81e7c91fecd6c9831d/68747470733a2f2f6d656469612e67697068792e636f6d2f6d656469612f5a784c624c76557434394f3057744c4575662f67697068792e676966\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Refrence: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://android-arsenal.com/</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Libs And Tools','','inherit','closed','closed','','201-revision-v1','','','2019-01-05 10:31:08','2019-01-05 10:31:08','',201,'http://blogs.appsfeature.com/index.php/2019/01/05/201-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(223,1,'2019-01-05 10:50:16','2019-01-05 10:50:16','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7357\">EasyFlipViewPager</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a 