"_blank\">https://github.com/DMGDesignUK/DmgLocationUtils</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/armcha/DebugBanner?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7090\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/armcha/DebugBanner</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/mrgames13/DrawingActivity?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7098\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/mrgames13/DrawingActivity</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/bitvale/DroidMotion?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7104\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/bitvale/DroidMotion</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyValidation?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7109\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyValidation</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/mjn1369/FieldSetView?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7030\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/mjn1369/FieldSetView</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/maayyaannkk/ImagePicker?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7055\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/maayyaannkk/ImagePicker</a></li><li> <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/himangipatel/ImagesPreview?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=6979\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/himangipatel/ImagesPreview</a> </li><li> <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/jaiselrahman/FilePicker?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7002\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/jaiselrahman/FilePicker</a> </li><li> <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/shagiz/AsyncFilePicker?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7011\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/shagiz/AsyncFilePicker</a> </li><li></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Refrence: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://android-arsenal.com/</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Libs And Tools','','inherit','closed','closed','','201-revision-v1','','','2019-01-05 12:57:57','2019-01-05 12:57:57','',201,'http://blogs.appsfeature.com/index.php/2019/01/05/201-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(256,1,'2019-01-05 13:05:12','2019-01-05 13:05:12','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7357\">EasyFlipViewPager</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/book_flip_demo.gif?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7357\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/poker_demo.gif?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7357\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/gallery_demo.gif?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7357\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><h2></h2><br><img width=\"280px\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/gallery_demo.gif\"></a><img width=\"280px\"  hspace=\"20\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/poker_demo.gif\"><img width=\"280px\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wajahatkarim3/EasyFlipViewPager/master/Art/book_flip_demo.gif\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7359\">Hauler</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Hauler is a library containing custom layout which enables to easily create swipe to dismiss&nbsp;<code>Activity</code>. Implementation is based on code from project&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/nickbutcher/plaid?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7359\" target=\"_blank\">Plaid</a>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/thefuntasty/hauler\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/thefuntasty/hauler</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n \n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/thefuntasty/hauler/master/images/example.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:300px;\"></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7362\">Easy CSV</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Creates csv file for android </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/hsmnzaydn/easy-csv\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/hsmnzaydn/easy-csv</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7364\">Text Scanner from image</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> This library extend&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://developers.google.com/vision/?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7364\" target=\"_blank\">google vision</a>&nbsp;. And initilay it read text from image. for reading text from image you have to give image&nbsp;<strong>Uri</strong>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<strong>Bitmap</strong>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/mahimrocky/TextRecognizer\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/mahimrocky/TextRecognizer</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mahimrocky/TextRecognizer/master/screenshot.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:300px;\"></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7366\">Choreographer</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Animate views easily by chaining animations, run them serially or in parallel. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/ZachBublil/Choreographer\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/ZachBublil/Choreographer</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ZachBublil/Choreographer/master/demoGif.gif\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7367\">BottomSheetTimeRangePicker</a></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>BottomSheetPickers is a tiny Android library for adding Date and Time Pickers as Modal BottomSheetDialogs with From and To ranges.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The library is inspired by Titto Jose\'s&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/tittojose/TimeRangePicker?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7367\" target=\"_blank\">TimeRangePicker</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/adawoud/BottomSheetTimeRangePicker\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/adawoud/BottomSheetTimeRangePicker</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adawoud/BottomSheetTimeRangePicker/master/art/bottomsheetpicker.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:300px;\"></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7376\">android-imagecropview</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> An Android library that lets you implement image crop. ImageCropView crops image by moving image under fixed crop area like instagram and iOS. Image zoom in/out is base on&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/sephiroth74/ImageViewZoom?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7376\" target=\"_blank\">sephiroth74\'s imageViewZoom. Sample app is base on&nbsp;</a><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://developers.aviary.com/?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7376\" target=\"_blank\">aviary SDK sample.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/naver/android-imagecropview\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/naver/android-imagecropview</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/naver/android-imagecropview/master/doc/img/pholar.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:300px;\"></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7417\">Payment Card View</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/manojbhadane/PaymentCardView\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/manojbhadane/PaymentCardView</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/manojbhadane/PaymentCardView/master/PaymentCardView.png\" alt=\"\"/><figcaption><br></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7407\">Dynamic Toasts</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/hotstu/ZebraTextView\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/hotstu/ZebraTextView</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> A simple library to display themed toasts with icon and text on Android 9+ (Gingerbread or above) devices. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/pranavpandey/dynamic-toasts/master/graphics/dynamic-toasts-preview.png\" alt=\"\"/><figcaption><br></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7401\">Material Toast</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/marcoscgdev/MaterialToast\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/marcoscgdev/MaterialToast</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nA fully and highly customizable material designed Toast for Android.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/marcoscgdev/MaterialToast/master/device-2018-12-22-164932.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:300px;\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1> <a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7351\">StateViews</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/kobeumut/StateViews\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/kobeumut/StateViews</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Create &amp; Show progress, data or error views, the easy way! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kobeumut/StateViews/master/art/StatusPage.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7334\">Country code dialog picker</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://github.com/BartNijland91/android-countrycodepickerdialog\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/BartNijland91/android-countrycodepickerdialog</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BartNijland91/android-countrycodepickerdialog/master/screenshot.png\" alt=\"\"style=\"width:300px;\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7340\">Cyanea</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/jaredrummler/Cyanea\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/jaredrummler/Cyanea</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nA powerful, dynamic, and fun theme engine. Named after Octopus Cyanea which is adept at camouflage and not only can change color frequently, but also can change the patterns on and texture of its skin.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\">\n<a>\n<img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/7f7f7520d61f2f704ff12d6d31b7cafe601263e4/68747470733a2f2f692e696d6775722e636f6d2f6543366435574f2e676966\" alt=\"\"/>\n</a>\n<a>\n<img align=\"left\" hspace=\"10\" src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/b0cdc1242d8170b8184ef2a92d8afd5af4152563/68747470733a2f2f692e696d6775722e636f6d2f706a44456a576c2e676966\">\n</a>\n</figure> \n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/3/7342\">CurvedBottomNavigationView</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/androidtutorialonline/CurvedBottomNavigationView\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/androidtutorialonline/CurvedBottomNavigationView</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nwe will learn How to draw custom shapes in Curved Bottom Navigation View\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/7cf1dee61362f29a0abd06248d8b439a5323130f/68747470733a2f2f7777772e616e64726f69647475746f7269616c6f6e6c696e652e636f6d2f77702d636f6e74656e742f75706c6f6164732f323031382f31312f426f74746f6d4e617669676174696f6e566965772e676966\" alt=\"enter image description here\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7350\">FloatingToast</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/hariprasanths/FloatingToast\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/hariprasanths/FloatingToast</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nAn android library to make customisable floating animated toasts\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/b469bd7e9f684420b89eab81e7c91fecd6c9831d/68747470733a2f2f6d656469612e67697068792e636f6d2f6d656469612f5a784c624c76557434394f3057744c4575662f67697068792e676966\" alt=\"\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7306\">Hidden SearchView in RecyclerView</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/lnicolet/HiddenSearchWithRecyclerView\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/lnicolet/HiddenSearchWithRecyclerView</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> An easy way to search in your recycler view without having an always-on display search view. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lnicolet/HiddenSearchWithRecyclerView/master/default_example.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:300px;\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7316\">SMS view</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/VRGsoftUA/SmsView\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/VRGsoftUA/SmsView</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/VRGsoftUA/SmsView/master/preview.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:300px;\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7320\">CameraViewEx</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/pvasa/cameraview-ex\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/pvasa/cameraview-ex</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nCameraViewEx makes integration of camera implementation and various camera features into any Android project very easy.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nCameraViewEx requires minimum API level 14. The library uses Camera1 API on API Level 14-20 and Camera2 on API level 21 and above.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7292\">Android Scratchcard</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/myinnos/AndroidScratchCard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/myinnos/AndroidScratchCard</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nLight Weighted Scratchcard View Library for Android\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/myinnos/AndroidScratchCard/master/images-gif/androidscratchcard-example.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:300px;\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7278\">AndroidVeil</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/skydoves/AndroidVeil\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/skydoves/AndroidVeil</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A library that lets you implement skeletons and shimmer animation for veiling layouts and recyclerView.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\">\n\n<p><a href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/24237865/47777293-c736d780-dd37-11e8-9107-5242746a7b8c.gif?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7278\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/24237865/47777293-c736d780-dd37-11e8-9107-5242746a7b8c.gif\"  hspace=\"20\" ></a> <a href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/24237865/47781860-1aae2300-dd42-11e8-8c5c-a2417b03b74d.gif?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7278\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/24237865/47781860-1aae2300-dd42-11e8-8c5c-a2417b03b74d.gif\"></a></p>\n\n</figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7281\">ParallaxView</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/VRGsoftUA/ParallaxView\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/VRGsoftUA/ParallaxView</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nView container which applies parallax effect to its content. You can Even achieve 3d effect if you use two containers, one atop another like on video below.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\">\n<a href=\"https://github.com/VRGsoftUA/ParallaxView/blob/master/scroll1.gif?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7281\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" ></a><a href=\"https://github.com/VRGsoftUA/ParallaxView/blob/master/scroll2.gif?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7281\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img width=\"270\" height=\"480\"   hspace=\"20\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/VRGsoftUA/ParallaxView/master/scroll2.gif\"></a><img width=\"270\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/VRGsoftUA/ParallaxView/master/scroll1.gif\"><br><br> \n\n</figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7282\">WP7ProgressBar</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/shadowalker77/wp7progressbar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/shadowalker77/wp7progressbar</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nThis library aims to bring awesome windows phone 7 and windows 10 progress bar to android applications. Here is the example:\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/shadowalker77/wp7progressbar/master/ScreenShots/wp10.gif\" alt=\"\"  hspace=\"20\" />\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/shadowalker77/wp7progressbar/master/ScreenShots/wp7.gif\">\n</figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7287\">SimpleSearchView</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Ferfalk/SimpleSearchView\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/Ferfalk/SimpleSearchView</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A simple SearchView for Android based on Material Design</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>API 16+&nbsp;<em>(Reveal animation for API 21 and above, fade animation otherwise)</em></li><li>Two styles</li><li>Option to hide TabLayout automatically when it opens</li><li>Text and animations listeners</li><li>Customization options</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\">\n<p><a href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13675455/46987845-4091c180-d0cc-11e8-8904-87f3c24d4c0a.gif?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7287\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img width=\"360\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13675455/46987845-4091c180-d0cc-11e8-8904-87f3c24d4c0a.gif\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13675455/46987873-60c18080-d0cc-11e8-8d10-2b8cf8a4124b.gif?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7287\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img width=\"360\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/13675455/46987873-60c18080-d0cc-11e8-8d10-2b8cf8a4124b.gif\"></a></p>\n</figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7240\">Andrutil</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/ShabanKamell/andrutil\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/ShabanKamell/andrutil</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>Useful Android Utilities.</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Available Utils:</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:code -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>ActivityUtil\nAppUtil\nBackStackUtil\nBottomNavigationViewUtil\nCallback\nDateUtil\nDiskStorageUtil\nFragmentManagerUtil\nFunc\nGsonUtil\nHtmlUtil\nKeyboardUtil\nKeyguardManagerUtil\nLocaleUtil\nMediaPlayerUtil\nObservableUtil\nPackageInfoUtil\nPhoneUtil\nRecyclerViewUtil\nRtlConfigUtil\nServiceUtil\nSpaceItemDecoration\nSystemOverlayUtil\nToastUtil\nWindowUtil\nVectorDrawableUtil\nDrawableUtil</code></pre>\n<!-- /wp:code -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7244\">DotLoadersPack</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/agrawalsuneet/DotLoadersPack-Android\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/agrawalsuneet/DotLoadersPack-Android</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/12999622/39367184-f3bb706a-4a2d-11e8-9120-5027bbef2861.gif\" alt=\"\"  hspace=\"20\" />\n\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/12999622/36224573-f274b956-11bf-11e8-8f97-e4c031959465.gif\">\n</figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7248\">EasyAbout</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/marcoscgdev/EasyAbout\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/marcoscgdev/EasyAbout</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nA fully material-designed about fragment for your application.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/marcoscgdev/EasyAbout/master/screenshots/1.png\" alt=\"Sample App\" style=\"max-width:25%;\" />\n \n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/marcoscgdev/EasyAbout/master/screenshots/2.png\" alt=\"Sample App\" style=\"max-width:25%;\" hspace=\"20\" />\n \n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/marcoscgdev/EasyAbout/master/screenshots/3.png\" alt=\"Sample App\" style=\"max-width:25%;\"/>\n\n</figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7057\">ScatterImageView</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/SIMMORSAL/ScatterImageView\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/SIMMORSAL/ScatterImageView</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nA library that scatters some ImageViews around haphazardly, or orderly\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/24822099/42732838-5a9cd2b8-883d-11e8-8463-aefee1f2be11.gif\" alt=\"\"style=\"max-width:100%;\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/7058\">ReadMoreOption</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/devendroid/ReadMoreOption\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/devendroid/ReadMoreOption</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\n\nConvert your TextView in ExpandableTextView with added options ReadMore/ReadLess.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/devendroid/ReadMoreOption/master/assets/rmo-1.0.0.gif\" alt=\"\"style=\"max-width:100%;\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://android-arsenal.com/details/1/6996\">TypeWriterView</a></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/skymansandy/typewriterview/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">https://github.com/skymansandy/typewriterview/</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>A simple Android library for typewriter like effects</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Features:</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Animate contents of textview as if it were typed by a TypeWriter</li><li>Set Animation Text appearance duration</li><li>Set TypeWriter sound effect (With or without sound)</li><li>Set Typing animation listeners (4 available)</li><li>Set all the usual attributes of TextView and style your view.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/skymansandy/typewriterview/master/art/demoTypeWriterView.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:300px;\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Github Important Links:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://github.com/mmoamenn/AnimationsPlus?utm_source=android-arsenal.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=7251\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/mmoamenn/AnimationsPlus</a></li><li><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=